Makefile

# The Mobiles/ tree is unrelated to the backend Docker image (the final
# image only contains the Go binary). Excluding it from the build context
# avoids transferring ~10GB of mobile build artifacts to the Docker daemon
# on every build, which both slows builds down and can fill the builder
# VM's disk. Has no effect on git or what's in the repo.
Mobiles
